[I] A user friendly version control system front-end

[T] Cervisia is a user friendly version control system front-end. The aim is to
[T] support CVS and other version control system programs in a unified
[T] interface, featuring conflict resolution, difference and history viewers,
[T] status for the working copy files, and support for most version control
[T] functions.

[U] https://www.kde.org

